{"tid":906570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國農業部 : 740萬人返鄉創業 振興農村 !!!!!!!!","createTime":"2018-11-18T06:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T15:45:38.000Z","uid":54733,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8b70122c3a4f4566583cf2d64a03d46286ce0f","tid":906570,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:03:57.000Z","msg":"中國農業部日前公布一組數字稱，中國返鄉下鄉創業創新人員已累計達740萬人，成為鄉村振興的新生力量，顯然很正面。但懷疑真相到底如何的聲音很不少，有人甚至發問：&ldquo;你當民工是傻子？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n網上有人議論，別把農民工返鄉潮改了一個好聽的名字來粉飾，還有人把這種現象和中國目前的經濟形勢連在一起，大量私企破產，許多人無出路，農民工只得返鄉。有人評論稱，這些返鄉下鄉人員，轉換個身份，其實就是&ldquo;失業人員&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n中國農業部為人們展現的是一幅新農村的景象，由於當局&ldquo;近年來大力促進新農民新技術創新&rdquo;&ldquo;新農民群體不斷壯大&rdquo;，&ldquo;新產業快速發展&rdquo;，&ldquo;新技術日新月異&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n中共前總書記趙紫陽的秘書鮑彤發推說：農民工回鄉潮的掀起，是農村繁榮超過了城市的標誌---畫時代的標誌。換言之，標誌着城市繁榮已經比不上農村的轉折點。<br />\n<br />\n這事情與城市清理低端人口有沒有關係呢，所以他們不得不返鄉？<br />\n<br />\n這幾年農民工回鄉潮不斷，有人評論，那是因為大多數第一代打工的干不動了，或家裡老人要照顧了，或子女要成家帶孫子了，沒市場，沒關係，經濟下行，回鄉創業的十有八九是死，把打工掙的這點錢虧乾淨，還欠一身外債。還有人說，城市房租高漲，生活艱難，花去小孩學費，一年到頭所剩無幾，只要老家能有一點點活路，何必出來混，還遭人歧視。<br />\n<br />\n當然也有返鄉後很成功的，但那不是普遍的情形。<br />\n<br />\n不過，北京當局這次有意強調這次返鄉下鄉人員的年齡和&ldquo;素質&rdquo;，這次去農村的，不僅有還鄉的，還有下鄉的，裡面包括農民工、大學生、退役軍人和科研人員、平均年齡四十歲，高中以上學歷佔40%。"},{"pid":"e0eadae93581fdb71c0d6523a491434dff9ccd6a","tid":906570,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n贏了贏了"},{"pid":"46286c52c42b151f55ab2cb093a8c95a7f386c98","tid":906570,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:05:12.000Z","msg":"但有財經人士在社交媒體質疑，上述返鄉下鄉人員，轉換個身份，其實就是&ldquo;失業人員&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n多維引述一位粉絲達31萬的&ldquo;顏值財經程凌虛&rdquo;的財經博主說，新失業人員高達740萬，正好與有報道的今年上半年倒閉企業504萬家的數據相吻合。明明是大規模失業，卻偏說返鄉創業，&ldquo;你當民工是傻子？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n這一上半年企業倒閉的數字有待核實，網易也有一篇報道稱，上半年504萬家企業倒閉，但稱失業人數超過200萬。<br />\n<br />\n但是中國經濟數月以來不太景氣是事實，星期五中國有媒體報道說，由於受國家金融危機的衝擊，大量工廠關閉，結果使今年的民工返鄉潮提前拉開了序幕。<br />\n<br />\n不少分析人士更認為中美貿易戰的效應開始發作，民營企業生存艱難。這從最近從習近平也忽然不斷地為民營經濟背書可窺一斑。<br />\n<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/中國/20181113-北京稱七百多萬人返鄉下鄉振興農村惹疑\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F20181113-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%83%E7%99%BE%E5%A4%9A%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%94%E9%84%89%E4%B8%8B%E9%84%89%E6%8C%AF%E8%88%88%E8%BE%B2%E6%9D%91%E6%83%B9%E7%96%91&d=tg3Dda7iVq8UyaQIpyYsBACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5f7d3b1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/中國/20181113-北京稱七百多萬人返鄉下鄉振興農村惹疑</a>"},{"pid":"ab0b765dc1d9e6b96cf1fae10b576c0f1592c737","tid":906570,"uid":54733,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"返鄉下搞start-up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國又贏"},{"pid":"ebecd9e93b2fb69d321882e0d9025e32c4e3e2ec","tid":906570,"uid":54516,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:12:14.000Z","msg":"白事當紅事辦"},{"pid":"1cf2fe522077dddd141afb78a1f216637263a566","tid":906570,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b21b233351546f54218e029c47e32d6a46e192e","tid":906570,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:23:35.000Z","msg":"人有多大膽<br />\n<br />\n一齊冚家鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ce1a5aa38f52b9e85328bcd97283917e8b118c","tid":906570,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:27:44.000Z","msg":"養竹鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d0e6cf70e07ce6584487d4ae895d02756f8ebf","tid":906570,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:31:30.000Z","msg":"上山下鄉"},{"pid":"3423557acbc04506e3b967dd46eee0a19ea085f6","tid":906570,"uid":62011,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"10d0e6cf70e07ce6584487d4ae895d02756f8ebf","tid":906570,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:31:30.000Z","msg":"上山下鄉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:44:24.000Z","msg":"上山下鄉2.0"},{"pid":"e0532a4e2ca179639e994b1c51e8d9811636013f","tid":906570,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864c33426276308e4954179f2c927b3dfb702c3e","tid":906570,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c428997a02262e39e0dfa87129b67f108905dd9","tid":906570,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fcc43ff95f78ac09ce7cf3e752c276bfa00027","tid":906570,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb03250e274c1b45a1f2ff50d90a37b106f03ca","tid":906570,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:39:50.000Z","msg":"調你農務臭系"},{"pid":"2897332c8d75a3ac98023e888916716b8858256d","tid":906570,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"返鄉養竹鼠"},{"pid":"0568e654183a02fde8fd8bff033a74ba55410725","tid":906570,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:34:17.000Z","msg":"返鄉下搞kick start <br />\n呀唔係 叫咩眾籌"},{"pid":"2d161551224dc160ed2d637ec590cbac8fe01e7d","tid":906570,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1078945aac236b91b4d846772c06f87aba1e3002","tid":906570,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/kinghungip/1387821402-1387551105_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fkinghungip%2F1387821402-1387551105_n.jpg&h=1dcf5e96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfd6fdeebaa98a19d56c841c83453dceaae6a7ce","tid":906570,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:44:49.000Z","msg":"港人唔好笑，鎖完你地下場仲慘烈"},{"pid":"8df21a89313e3b19fbc6ac5d08fb76caa53e8938","tid":906570,"uid":119409,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"有冇誇大就唔知<br />\n但事實上好多民工返去鄉下搞網店<br />\n內陸好多野成本又低<br />\n價錢平消費者多左好多分貨揀<br />\n而對班民工黎講收入都比以前高呢個係事實<br />\n而且點解一二線城市咁多中小企業做唔店<br />\n唔係佢地汁粒所以D人失業<br />\n而係依家冇咩人肯做工人<br />\n人工升左都冇人愈黎愈少人去做，呢個都係事實<br />\n但連登仔是但一句 &quot;是謊言&quot; 就自己打晒飛機咁開心<br />\n其實有幾多人真係諗下可信性<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 工作上經常要同D大陸廠有接觸"}]}